trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.ITemplate"></xref> implementation that is called from the generated page class code.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Web.UI.ITemplate"> </xref>从生成的页类代码调用的实现。

trans-unit.source: The CompiledTemplateBuilder class is used by ASP.NET to create a template for a templated control from the generated class code.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET 使用 CompiledTemplateBuilder 类生成的类代码中创建的模板化控件模板。

trans-unit.source: It is not meant to be used directly in your code.
trans-unit.target: 但并不是在代码中直接使用。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.CompiledTemplateBuilder"></xref> class.
This constructor is used internally by ASP.NET to create a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.CompiledTemplateBuilder> class.
trans-unit.target: 此构造函数在内部用于 asp.net 创建的新实例的<xref:System.Web.UI.CompiledTemplateBuilder>类。</xref:System.Web.UI.CompiledTemplateBuilder>

trans-unit.source: It is not meant to be used directly in your code.
trans-unit.target: 但并不是在代码中直接使用。

trans-unit.source: A delegate used to handle the <xref:System.Web.UI.CompiledTemplateBuilder.InstantiateIn*> method call.
Populates the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"></xref> object with the child controls contained in the template.
trans-unit.target: 填充<xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"></xref>模板中包含的子控件的对象。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.CompiledBindableTemplateBuilder.InstantiateIn%2A> method is the <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateBuilder> class's implementation of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ITemplate.InstantiateIn%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
It is used by ASP.NET to create the control hierarchy of the template and is not meant to be used directly in your code.
trans-unit.target: 它 ASP.NET 用来创建模板的控件层次结构，并不是在代码中直接使用。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"></xref> that represents the container used to store the child controls in the template.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"> </xref>表示用于在模板中存储子控件的容器。
